Package: RpsiScan
Type: Package
Title: Perform pseudouridylation identification from high-throughput reverse transcription stop sequencing data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zhirong Chen
Maintainer: The package maintainer <chenzhr23@mail2.sysu.edu.cn>
Description: Pseudouridylation identification using command line tool--'psiScan'.
  psiScan accept CMC/Input bam file to perform reverse transcriptopn stop arithmetic e.g treatPreRpmFold,preRpmFoldRatio,treatAfterRpmFold,afterRpmFoldRatio,treatStopRatio,stopRatioFC.
  psiScan R package API enhances access to psiScan as well as offers additional utilities for Pseudouridylation identification.
License: GPL-2
Imports: data.table, dplyr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: Preferred genomic operations engine: 'psiScan', 'bedtools'
